%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor ADMIN as Admin
participant UI as Vendor Management UI
participant BFF as Vendor BFF
participant CACHE as Redis Cache
participant VMS as Vendor Management Service
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}
participant AUDIT as Audit Service

ADMIN ->> UI: Open Evaluation Model Setup
UI ->> BFF: Load setup screen

BFF ->> CACHE: Get active vendor evaluation config
alt Cache Hit
    CACHE -->> BFF: Stage, criteria, rating scale, rules
else Cache Miss
    BFF ->> VMS: getEvaluationModel()
    VMS ->> READDB: Get Vendor details
    READDB -->> VMS: Existing config / blank setup
    VMS -->> BFF: Config response
    BFF ->> CACHE: Cache config
end

BFF -->> UI: Render setup screen

ADMIN ->> UI: Add/update stage, criteria,<br/> weights, rating scale, acceptance rules
ADMIN ->> UI: Click Save
UI ->> BFF: Save evaluation model payload

BFF ->> VMS: validateEvaluationModel(payload)
VMS ->> VMS: Validate mandatory stage, criteria rows, <br/>weightage, unique score, parseable rules

alt Validation Failed
    VMS -->> BFF: Validation errors
    BFF -->> UI: Show inline errors
else Validation Passed
    BFF ->> VMS: saveEvaluationModel(payload)
    VMS ->> PRIMARYDB: UPSERT vendor_stage_master
    VMS ->> PRIMARYDB: UPSERT vendor_eval_criteria
    VMS ->> PRIMARYDB: UPSERT vendor_rating_scale
    VMS ->> PRIMARYDB: UPSERT vendor_acceptance_rule
    VMS ->> PRIMARYDB: INSERT vendor_workflow_audit <br/>(action='SAVE_CONFIG', stage='CONFIG_SAVED')
    VMS -->> BFF: Save success

    VMS ->> KAFKA: Publish VendorEvaluationConfigSaved
    VMS ->> AUDIT: Log admin configuration change
    BFF ->> CACHE: Invalidate vendor evaluation config cache
    BFF -->> UI: Show save confirmation
end